{"id":"55cc5f344e3bd2ce7bd42a99c1a9441f45bb6b23","axis":"silent","repo":"SBoudrias/Inquirer.js","sha":"55cc5f344e3bd2ce7bd42a99c1a9441f45bb6b23","parsed":{"files":[{"path":".github/workflows/main.yml","lines":["@@ -54,7 +54,7 @@ jobs:","       - run: yarn oxlint .","       - run: yarn oxfmt --check .","       - run: yarn eslint .","-      - run: yarn check:engines","+      - run: yarn package lint --check","       - name: Validate package setup","         run: |","           yarn setup"],"additions":1,"deletions":1,"truncated":false},{"path":"AGENTS.md","lines":["@@ -2,7 +2,7 @@"," "," ## Project Structure & Module Organization"," ","-The repo is a Yarn workspaces monorepo. Core runtime logic shared primitives and shared primitives live in `packages/core/src`, and individual prompt implementations under `packages/<prompt>/src`. Testing utilities sit in `packages/testing`, while `packages/demo` provides the interactive showcase. Integration suites reside in `integration/cjs` and `integration/esm` to verify bundling. Tooling scripts live in `tools/` and repo wiring (tsconfig, release helpers) in `internals/`. Treat `packages/*/dist` as generated output.","+The repo is a Yarn workspaces monorepo. Core runtime logic shared primitives and shared primitives live in `packages/core/src`, and individual prompt implementations under `packages/<prompt>/src`. Testing utilities sit in `packages/testing`, while `packages/demo` provides the interactive showcase. Integration suites reside in `integration/cjs` and `integration/esm` to verify bundling. Tooling scripts and repo wiring (tsconfig, release helpers) live in `tools/`. Treat `packages/*/dist` and `tools/*/dist` as generated output."," "," ## Build, Test, and Development Commands"," "],"additions":1,"deletions":1,"truncated":false},{"path":"eslint.config.js","lines":["@@ -15,8 +15,8 @@ export default defineConfig(","       '.yarn',","       'packages/*/dist/**',","       'packages/*/node_modules/**',","-      'internals/*/di